   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 1084, recto: (1) A tremis has come to me from you, (2) Daniel (son of) Manasseh, for your demosion (3) for the second katabole of the (4) first year, total one-third solidus.  Written Payni 6, (5) indiction 1.  I, Laleu, the headman, sign (6) this receipt.  I, Psan, (7) drew up this receipt at his request.</ab>
